Constructor Detail

SaifReader

public SaifReader()

SaifReader

public SaifReader(File file)
Create a new SaifReader to read the SAIF archive from the specified file . If the file is a directory, then in must contain an expanded SAIF archive, otherwise the file must be a compressed SAIF archive (.zip or.saf).

Parameters:
file - The SAIF archive file to read.

SaifReader

public SaifReader(String fileName)
Create a new SaifReader to read the SAIF archive from the specified file name. If the file is a directory, then in must contain an expanded SAIF archive, otherwise the file must be a compressed SAIF archive (.zip or.saf).

Parameters:
fileName - The name of the SAIF archive file to read.
